1
00:01:30,970 --> 00:01:35,020
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,860 --> 00:01:39,310
[2006]

3
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:40,680
Auntie, I'm back.

4
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:41,410
You're back.

5
00:01:41,870 --> 00:01:43,070
What are you holding?

6
00:01:44,310 --> 00:01:45,350
This is our group's entry

7
00:01:45,350 --> 00:01:47,350
for the architectural model competition.

8
00:01:47,350 --> 00:01:48,310
I didn't finish my part,

9
00:01:48,310 --> 00:01:49,970
so I brought it back to work on.

10
00:01:50,350 --> 00:01:51,920
You're a senior in high school now.

11
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,759
You need to make the most of your time.

12
00:01:53,759 --> 00:01:54,840
Why participate in this competition

13
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,430
where you just play with toys?

14
00:01:56,430 --> 00:01:57,789
Focus on improving your grades,

15
00:01:57,789 --> 00:01:59,229
getting into a good college,

16
00:01:59,229 --> 00:02:01,690
and finding a good job—
that's what matters.

17
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:16,840
This isn't a toy.

18
00:02:17,870 --> 00:02:19,930
It's an architectural design model.

19
00:02:21,180 --> 00:02:24,190
[Episode 21:
A Dream I Never Dared to Have Before]

20
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:29,590
[Investigation Report]
[Wang Qiang, the Missing Worker]

21
00:02:30,190 --> 00:02:31,790
This is that missing worker?

22
00:02:32,910 --> 00:02:34,110
He ran off to Nanyang.

23
00:02:38,630 --> 00:02:40,430
So you had news all along.

24
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:41,960
Cheng.

25
00:02:43,190 --> 00:02:45,280
It's not that
I wouldn't let you investigate.

26
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:47,590
I know there's something fishy about this.

27
00:02:47,590 --> 00:02:48,870
But Nanyang is too chaotic.

28
00:02:48,870 --> 00:02:49,800
The waters are too deep there.

29
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,660
I didn't dare let you look into it.

30
00:02:53,470 --> 00:02:54,200
But you know,

31
00:02:55,470 --> 00:02:56,329
I won't give up.

32
00:02:56,430 --> 00:02:56,840
Right.

33
00:02:57,150 --> 00:02:57,680
I know.

34
00:02:59,030 --> 00:03:00,080
You look

35
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,620
docile on the outside,

36
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,560
but you're actually bold and driven,

37
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:05,400
with a fire burning inside.

38
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,310
If it weren't for

39
00:03:07,310 --> 00:03:08,470
that personality of yours,

40
00:03:08,470 --> 00:03:09,470
I wouldn't have invited you

41
00:03:09,470 --> 00:03:10,840
to join Zhiyuan in the first place.

42
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,750
And even if I had,

43
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:13,000
you wouldn't have given up

44
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,030
your stable job in Jingcheng

45
00:03:14,030 --> 00:03:16,090
and come to Shengcheng to work for me.

46
00:03:17,470 --> 00:03:17,930
Senior,

47
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,680
you really gave me

48
00:03:21,220 --> 00:03:22,750
an offer I couldn't refuse.

49
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:25,360
If I had stayed in Jingcheng
following the routine,

50
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,000
I wouldn't have been

51
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:26,960
taking cases this soon.

52
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:28,560
Alright, enough about that.

53
00:03:29,630 --> 00:03:30,890
Over the past few days,

54
00:03:31,090 --> 00:03:32,490
I've thought it through.

55
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:33,800
I can't take advantage

56
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,280
of your personality

57
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:37,000
while trying to turn you into

58
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,329
an obedient little boy.

59
00:03:40,430 --> 00:03:41,490
Handle this matter

60
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:42,970
however you see fit.

61
00:03:43,310 --> 00:03:43,970
However...

62
00:03:44,430 --> 00:03:45,230
I understand.

63
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,750
I'll definitely be careful.

64
00:03:46,750 --> 00:03:48,590
And I won't let it affect my other work.

65
00:03:48,590 --> 00:03:49,790
Don't worry, Senior.

66
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,400
Dingsheng cake?

67
00:03:58,079 --> 00:03:59,280
I like the meaning of it—victory.

68
00:03:59,280 --> 00:03:59,960
We lawyers

69
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,290
should eat more of this.

70
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:04,660
Mr. Mao, this way, please.

71
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:09,330
This way.

72
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,360
I heard from many clients

73
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,960
that for some small projects,

74
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:14,680
you seem to be

75
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,910
slacking off a bit now.

76
00:04:15,910 --> 00:04:16,750
That won't do.

77
00:04:20,750 --> 00:04:22,190
This is my uncle, Liu Yong.

78
00:04:22,190 --> 00:04:24,430
He's the General Manager
of Yuanhui Decoration.

79
00:04:24,430 --> 00:04:24,850
Alright.

80
00:04:24,850 --> 00:04:26,700
He came to Shengcheng in 1984

81
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,560
and formed a renovation team,

82
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:30,070
doing interior decoration.

83
00:04:30,070 --> 00:04:31,600
After winning the bid for the guesthouse,

84
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,530
he started doing bigger projects.

85
00:04:34,270 --> 00:04:35,880
So for this bid,

86
00:04:35,950 --> 00:04:37,240
you're also participating

87
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,390
under the name of your uncle's company?

88
00:04:38,390 --> 00:04:38,800
Yes.

89
00:04:39,159 --> 00:04:40,240
But after this,

90
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:40,870
I plan to do it

91
00:04:40,870 --> 00:04:42,470
under my own company's name.

92
00:04:43,190 --> 00:04:45,020
This is my office area.

93
00:04:48,130 --> 00:04:50,100
Let's go in and take a look, shall we?

94
00:04:50,100 --> 00:04:50,500
Okay.

95
00:04:50,530 --> 00:04:51,310
Okay, this way.

96
00:04:51,310 --> 00:04:52,070
As for the design,

97
00:04:52,070 --> 00:04:52,870
this place...

98
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,070
Yes, this...

99
00:04:54,070 --> 00:04:55,310
Yes, this is probably

100
00:04:55,750 --> 00:04:56,800
inside the private suite.

101
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:57,360
Ms. Xia?

102
00:04:58,330 --> 00:04:59,810
M... Mr. Mao!

103
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,270
Mr. Mao.

104
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:02,810
It really is Mr. Mao.

105
00:05:04,430 --> 00:05:06,390
It seems I don't need to introduce you.

106
00:05:06,390 --> 00:05:07,040
Mr. Mao,

107
00:05:07,310 --> 00:05:08,480
these are the studio's

108
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,360
current staff.

109
00:05:10,510 --> 00:05:11,510
This is Gong Yang.

110
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,360
Hello, Mr. Mao.

111
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,920
He's from the Oil Painting Department
at the Academy of Fine Arts.

112
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:16,380
He's been with me
since the guesthouse days.

113
00:05:16,430 --> 00:05:17,480
This is Hou Qi.

114
00:05:17,870 --> 00:05:19,430
She used to work

115
00:05:19,430 --> 00:05:19,950
at the Jiangcheng Design Institute.

116
00:05:19,950 --> 00:05:20,950
She is his senior.

117
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:21,630
After resigning,

118
00:05:21,630 --> 00:05:22,690
she came to join us.

119
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,070
As for the rest,

120
00:05:24,070 --> 00:05:25,070
they are all

121
00:05:25,070 --> 00:05:26,310
students who haven't graduated yet.

122
00:05:26,310 --> 00:05:27,310
They're interning here

123
00:05:27,310 --> 00:05:28,480
to see if they're interested.

124
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,950
Hello, Mr. Mao.

125
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,360
Hello, everyone.

126
00:05:33,070 --> 00:05:34,270
Oh, right. Let's make way.

127
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:34,870
Mr. Mao,

128
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,360
this is some of our

129
00:05:36,390 --> 00:05:37,450
rough design work.

130
00:05:46,500 --> 00:05:47,940
It is indeed very rough.

131
00:05:48,510 --> 00:05:49,190
So, Mr. Mao,

132
00:05:49,190 --> 00:05:50,950
we are eager

133
00:05:50,950 --> 00:05:52,409
to receive your guidance.

134
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,060
Alright, alright.

135
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:55,480
Mr. Mao, let them discuss.

136
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,390
Let's talk inside.

137
00:05:56,390 --> 00:05:56,750
Okay.

138
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,750
Mr. Mao is so handsome.

139
00:06:01,870 --> 00:06:02,390
Mr. Mao,

140
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:03,310
please have a seat.

141
00:06:03,310 --> 00:06:03,720
Okay.

142
00:06:18,630 --> 00:06:19,300
Have some tea.

143
00:06:19,300 --> 00:06:19,900
Thank you.

144
00:06:24,430 --> 00:06:25,720
On the way here,

145
00:06:25,950 --> 00:06:28,950
you made me look at
those construction sites on purpose.

146
00:06:28,950 --> 00:06:30,040
You said this place

147
00:06:30,060 --> 00:06:32,120
is full of opportunities and dreams.

148
00:06:32,630 --> 00:06:34,360
But have you thought about one thing?

149
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:36,070
It is also full of

150
00:06:36,950 --> 00:06:38,680
helplessness and reality.

151
00:06:39,390 --> 00:06:41,630
You have talent and luck.

152
00:06:42,310 --> 00:06:44,370
But what about those people outside?

153
00:06:44,870 --> 00:06:46,270
Do they have your talent

154
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:47,400
and opportunities?

155
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:48,680
I admit

156
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:51,070
that being able to
get to where I am today

157
00:06:51,070 --> 00:06:52,800
makes me one in a million lucky.

158
00:06:53,870 --> 00:06:54,750
But this doesn't conflict with

159
00:06:54,750 --> 00:06:56,010
my original intention

160
00:06:56,070 --> 00:06:57,470
of starting this studio.

161
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,740
I'm not boasting about

162
00:06:58,870 --> 00:07:00,750
being responsible for anyone's future.

163
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:02,120
How far they can go in the future

164
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,450
depends on themselves.

165
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,950
I just hope this studio

166
00:07:06,630 --> 00:07:08,270
can become their opportunity

167
00:07:08,270 --> 00:07:08,950
and luck.

168
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,070
In that case,

169
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:14,080
my trip won't be in vain.

170
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:17,240
That's what you called "not boasting"?

171
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:19,520
Since you went to my house,

172
00:07:20,190 --> 00:07:22,680
you've been talking big the whole time.

173
00:07:23,510 --> 00:07:24,270
But you still

174
00:07:24,270 --> 00:07:25,800
came to Shengcheng with me.

175
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:27,490
Even if you just take a look,

176
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,750
I'm already very grateful.

177
00:07:28,750 --> 00:07:31,000
I'm here for Haihua Hotel.

178
00:07:31,270 --> 00:07:33,920
I designed the proposal for Haihua Hotel.

179
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,500
I have to take responsibility

180
00:07:35,500 --> 00:07:36,560
for my own project.

181
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:38,890
I can't let you make changes
as you please.

182
00:07:41,960 --> 00:07:43,230
Tell me your ideas.

183
00:07:43,510 --> 00:07:44,600
I'm all ears.

184
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,280
Just a moment.

185
00:07:59,830 --> 00:08:01,960
We've visited the construction site.

186
00:08:02,070 --> 00:08:03,430
The hotel's main structure

187
00:08:03,430 --> 00:08:04,900
is basically complete

188
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:07,240
and is just waiting for decoration.

189
00:08:07,270 --> 00:08:08,160
I've also reviewed the proposal

190
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:09,420
you provided earlier.

191
00:08:09,510 --> 00:08:11,310
The sail-style main building

192
00:08:11,390 --> 00:08:13,040
and the garden-style landscape.

193
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,390
The time Dongfeng Holdings gave us

194
00:08:14,390 --> 00:08:15,720
is actually very short.

195
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:16,680
So I plan to

196
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:18,680
just make adjustments

197
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:20,000
to the decoration's color scheme

198
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,310
to make the hotel's style

199
00:08:21,310 --> 00:08:23,390
look more comfortable and casual

200
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:25,080
and less business-like.

201
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,160
What do you think?

202
00:08:28,870 --> 00:08:29,950
It seems you've reviewed

203
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:31,600
quite a few domestic and international

204
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,000
hotel decoration cases.

205
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,970
That... that is quite a good attitude.

206
00:08:38,549 --> 00:08:39,870
You mean...

207
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:44,380
Just draw it according to your ideas.

208
00:08:45,270 --> 00:08:47,240
Between the design and execution,

209
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,040
there is a gap.

210
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:50,990
If there's anything
that can't be realized,

211
00:08:50,990 --> 00:08:52,700
I'll remind you in time.

212
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:56,140
Then about you joining the studio...

213
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,690
We'll discuss it later.

214
00:09:02,910 --> 00:09:04,200
The factory guy

215
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:04,670
was just about to

216
00:09:04,670 --> 00:09:06,000
hit me with his shovel.

217
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,840
I blocked it like this.

218
00:09:07,870 --> 00:09:08,750
Guess what happened?

219
00:09:08,750 --> 00:09:10,150
-What happened?
-What happened?

220
00:09:10,150 --> 00:09:10,720
Then I...

221
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:12,720
Your legs nearly gave out from fear!

222
00:09:12,730 --> 00:09:14,000
No, they didn't!

223
00:09:18,270 --> 00:09:19,440
Right, exactly.

224
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:22,080
They nearly gave out from fear
on the site!

225
00:09:22,340 --> 00:09:23,000
You two...

226
00:09:23,270 --> 00:09:25,020
You really showed up at the wrong time.

227
00:09:25,020 --> 00:09:26,840
You didn't let me brag a bit longer.

228
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,840
I hadn't gotten to the best part yet.

229
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:31,120
You think they actually believe you?

230
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,630
The real hero of that day

231
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:33,670
was San.

232
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:35,550
I made one phone call,

233
00:09:35,550 --> 00:09:37,600
and he came to help without hesitation.

234
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:38,800
That's true loyalty.

235
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:41,220
San, you didn't just come to our rescue,

236
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:43,080
you even personally brought us
extra dishes.

237
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,480
I run a restaurant, after all.

238
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,750
Cooking a few extra dishes
to bring over...

239
00:09:45,750 --> 00:09:46,550
is no trouble.

240
00:09:47,670 --> 00:09:48,400
I have to say,

241
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,270
when I was a seaman,

242
00:09:50,390 --> 00:09:51,150
I thought sailing to Nanyang

243
00:09:51,150 --> 00:09:52,320
was dangerous enough.

244
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:52,910
I didn't expect that

245
00:09:52,910 --> 00:09:54,000
doing business in building materials

246
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:55,240
would be this dangerous too.

247
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:57,040
There are risks in any business.

248
00:09:57,270 --> 00:09:58,480
Zhenzhu, Wei,

249
00:09:58,870 --> 00:10:00,630
you two need to be more careful
in the future.

250
00:10:00,630 --> 00:10:02,630
Don't go investigating everything
by yourselves.

251
00:10:02,630 --> 00:10:03,870
We're a "tuandui."

252
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:06,000
There's no shame in asking for help.

253
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:08,650
It means "team."

254
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:10,870
Anyway,

255
00:10:11,030 --> 00:10:12,890
we really need to thank San again.

256
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:13,960
If you ever

257
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,000
need any help in the future,

258
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:16,400
I won't hesitate to help.

259
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:19,530
Why don't you two just swear brotherhood?

260
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:20,870
I think that's a great idea.

261
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:21,910
Swear brotherhood.

262
00:10:21,910 --> 00:10:22,390
Let's have a toast.

263
00:10:22,390 --> 00:10:23,080
Alright, let's drink to that.

264
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,150
Cheers.

265
00:10:24,390 --> 00:10:25,150
Welcome, San,

266
00:10:25,150 --> 00:10:26,270
to our team.

267
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:26,840
Great.

268
00:10:26,870 --> 00:10:28,550
Welcome!

269
00:10:32,510 --> 00:10:33,630
When are you two

270
00:10:33,910 --> 00:10:35,910
going to get your marriage license?

271
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:40,320
We've both been busy lately.

272
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:43,000
After the bidding
for Haihua Hotel is over,

273
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,400
we'll go get registered.

274
00:10:45,150 --> 00:10:45,750
By the way,

275
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,600
once we win the bid for the hotel,

276
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:49,360
our Happy Life Materials

277
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:51,150
will get another big deal, right?

278
00:10:51,150 --> 00:10:52,080
Not bad, Wei.

279
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,910
All you think about now is big deals.

280
00:10:53,910 --> 00:10:55,360
Of course.

281
00:10:55,550 --> 00:10:57,390
Big deals! Big deals!

282
00:11:02,390 --> 00:11:03,120
Alright then,

283
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:03,720
Young Master,

284
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,840
I'll get going then.

285
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:06,000
I'll report back if there's any news.

286
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:06,330
Okay.

287
00:11:09,150 --> 00:11:11,810
Second Young Master,
you're in Shengcheng too?

288
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:15,080
What is that loser doing here?

289
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:15,840
Why didn't you tell me

290
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:16,870
to arrange a reception?

291
00:11:16,870 --> 00:11:17,400
Mr. Meng.

292
00:11:17,790 --> 00:11:19,360
Daddy asked me to come on short notice

293
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:20,320
to handle some matters.

294
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:21,630
I'll definitely let you know
in advance next time.

295
00:11:21,630 --> 00:11:22,440
Okay, okay.

296
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:27,960
I'm leaving then.

297
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:32,970
Big Brother.

298
00:11:35,550 --> 00:11:36,150
By the way,

299
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:39,620
Daddy told me to ask you

300
00:11:39,630 --> 00:11:43,030
about the progress
of the shoe and clothing factory project.

301
00:11:43,030 --> 00:11:43,870
I

302
00:11:44,510 --> 00:11:46,310
will speak to the old man myself.

303
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:48,900
I don't need you to be a messenger.

304
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:52,240
Okay.

305
00:11:54,270 --> 00:11:55,790
I have an appointment,

306
00:11:56,150 --> 00:11:57,080
so I'll go in now.

307
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:58,920
I'll come find you when I'm done.

308
00:11:59,630 --> 00:12:01,290
Take care. I won't see you out.

309
00:12:02,870 --> 00:12:03,510
Loser.

310
00:12:04,870 --> 00:12:05,550
Building a factory

311
00:12:05,550 --> 00:12:06,480
is not that easy.

312
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:08,120
Why did the old man

313
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:08,840
send him here?

314
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:09,500
To scare me?

315
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:10,600
I don't know.

316
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:11,810
Have someone

317
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:13,030
keep a close eye on the group.

318
00:12:13,030 --> 00:12:13,360
Okay.

319
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:17,120
The shoe and clothing factory
takes too long to make a profit.

320
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:19,000
We must find a project

321
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:19,910
that yields results

322
00:12:19,910 --> 00:12:20,870
in the short term.

323
00:12:20,870 --> 00:12:22,670
Even a small project would work.

324
00:12:23,150 --> 00:12:24,360
Didn't Mr. Tang of Meihua

325
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:26,080
invest in a

326
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:27,400
five-star hotel in Shengcheng?

327
00:12:27,400 --> 00:12:28,280
Is there any opportunity for cooperation?

328
00:12:28,280 --> 00:12:29,520
Mr. Tang invested in

329
00:12:29,550 --> 00:12:30,390
Haihua Hotel.

330
00:12:30,510 --> 00:12:32,030
The exterior is finished,

331
00:12:32,030 --> 00:12:33,510
but the interior isn't.

332
00:12:34,550 --> 00:12:35,320
I remember now.

333
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:36,870
Last time, Liu Tianquan

334
00:12:37,030 --> 00:12:38,600
bid for that guesthouse

335
00:12:38,870 --> 00:12:40,200
to pave the way for this.

336
00:12:41,870 --> 00:12:43,720
He wanted to do the...

337
00:12:43,720 --> 00:12:45,380
decoration for Haihua Hotel.

338
00:12:46,890 --> 00:12:47,840
But you transferred him

339
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:49,030
to Gangdao.

340
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:50,960
Now we don't know the situation.

341
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:53,220
That damn loser actually has foresight.

342
00:12:54,550 --> 00:12:55,550
Arrange a meeting with the person

343
00:12:55,550 --> 00:12:56,270
in charge of Chengrong Tianchen.

344
00:12:56,270 --> 00:12:56,550
Okay.

345
00:12:56,550 --> 00:12:56,960
Also,

346
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:58,150
make an appointment

347
00:12:58,150 --> 00:12:58,950
with Mr. Tang.

348
00:12:58,960 --> 00:12:59,620
No problem.

349
00:13:02,910 --> 00:13:04,550
If you hadn't stopped them just now,

350
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:05,480
I think San

351
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:07,810
would have sworn brotherhood with Zhenzhu.

352
00:13:07,810 --> 00:13:08,720
I wonder when those two

353
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:09,840
will finally

354
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:10,910
confess their feelings.

355
00:13:10,910 --> 00:13:12,310
I think it's kinda tough.

356
00:13:12,390 --> 00:13:13,000
They probably

357
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:13,790
need something

358
00:13:13,790 --> 00:13:14,850
to give them a push.

359
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:16,600
Yeah. No rush.

360
00:13:16,970 --> 00:13:18,330
That day will come,

361
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:19,620
and so will that event.

362
00:13:21,270 --> 00:13:22,130
Let me quiz you.

363
00:13:22,750 --> 00:13:24,550
What event brought us together?

364
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:25,870
I'm not like San.

365
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:28,480
From the first time I saw you,

366
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:30,260
I knew you were the one.

367
00:13:30,500 --> 00:13:31,670
The Xia Xiaolan from Dahe Village,

368
00:13:31,670 --> 00:13:33,120
who was chased by a crowd,

369
00:13:33,670 --> 00:13:34,800
has been living here

370
00:13:36,550 --> 00:13:37,600
ever since.

371
00:13:39,970 --> 00:13:40,610
Really?

372
00:13:41,480 --> 00:13:42,280
Let me listen.

373
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:44,290
What am I doing in there?

374
00:13:46,550 --> 00:13:48,120
She seems to be saying

375
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:50,930
that she wants to stay here
for a lifetime.

376
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:53,120
Did I hear that right?

377
00:13:53,120 --> 00:13:53,720
Yes.

378
00:13:54,150 --> 00:13:55,010
For a lifetime.

379
00:14:02,390 --> 00:14:03,910
I always feel like this thing

380
00:14:03,910 --> 00:14:05,040
is important to you,

381
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:06,400
so I bought it for you.

382
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:09,150
It feels like fate.

383
00:14:10,270 --> 00:14:11,320
This alarm clock

384
00:14:11,870 --> 00:14:13,320
came back to me after all.

385
00:14:14,670 --> 00:14:16,200
It's like it's reminding me

386
00:14:17,400 --> 00:14:19,800
that I can't escape the destiny
of leaving.

387
00:14:20,630 --> 00:14:21,750
Did you think

388
00:14:21,870 --> 00:14:23,080
buying a clock was bad luck

389
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:24,320
the other day we were out?

390
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:25,920
Is that why you didn't buy it?

391
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:26,980
How about this?

392
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:28,530
Give me one yuan.

393
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:31,790
When I was young,

394
00:14:31,790 --> 00:14:33,050
my grandmother told me

395
00:14:33,150 --> 00:14:34,390
that if I gave her one yuan,

396
00:14:34,390 --> 00:14:35,270
it would be as if

397
00:14:35,270 --> 00:14:36,150
I had just bought it from her.

398
00:14:36,150 --> 00:14:37,280
Then all the bad luck

399
00:14:37,510 --> 00:14:38,710
would be washed away.

400
00:14:47,510 --> 00:14:48,170
Zhou Cheng.

401
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:49,720
Thank you.

402
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:53,150
I don't know

403
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:55,270
how long my lifetime here

404
00:14:55,270 --> 00:14:56,120
really is.

405
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:59,390
I just hope it will be long enough.

406
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,080
Long enough.

407
00:15:07,380 --> 00:15:08,170
This area—

408
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,600
how can we block it?

409
00:15:17,790 --> 00:15:18,650
Don't you think

410
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:20,630
changing Mr. Mao's plan

411
00:15:20,630 --> 00:15:21,360
right in front of him

412
00:15:21,360 --> 00:15:23,390
is a bit presumptuous of us?

413
00:15:23,670 --> 00:15:24,480
I don't know.

414
00:15:24,670 --> 00:15:26,630
If Ms. Xia says it's fine, it's fine.

415
00:15:26,630 --> 00:15:27,240
Besides,

416
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:28,480
we aren't changing much.

417
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:29,440
If you speak any louder,

418
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:30,870
I won't be able to hear you.

419
00:15:30,870 --> 00:15:32,000
I'm hard of hearing.

420
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:32,510
Mr. Mao.

421
00:15:32,510 --> 00:15:33,710
Mr. Mao, we're sorry.

422
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:35,440
What's there to be sorry for?

423
00:15:35,920 --> 00:15:37,780
Change whatever needs changing.

424
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:39,320
Your Ms. Xia has already

425
00:15:39,320 --> 00:15:40,720
paid my consulting fee anyway.

426
00:15:40,720 --> 00:15:42,120
I'm not losing anything.

427
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:44,260
Let's take a break, everyone.

428
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:46,200
The deadline for this plan is tight.

429
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:47,670
Thank you for your hard work
these past few days.

430
00:15:47,670 --> 00:15:49,030
Once the results are out,

431
00:15:49,030 --> 00:15:50,480
whether we win the bid or not,

432
00:15:50,480 --> 00:15:51,790
everyone gets a bonus.

433
00:15:52,390 --> 00:15:54,030
We'll definitely win!

434
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:55,770
If we win, double the bonus!

435
00:15:58,480 --> 00:15:59,270
Okay!

436
00:15:59,510 --> 00:16:00,040
Let's go.

437
00:16:01,030 --> 00:16:02,750
Here, help yourselves.

438
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:03,200
Okay.

439
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:04,750
Mr. Mao,

440
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:07,000
regarding the modifications to the plan,

441
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:09,330
I have an idea
I'd like to discuss with you.

442
00:16:09,490 --> 00:16:13,530
[Gangdao]

443
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:11,150
Shengcheng

444
00:16:11,360 --> 00:16:13,160
doesn't have a lounge this nice.

445
00:16:13,170 --> 00:16:15,500
Unlike me, you don't come back every week.

446
00:16:15,630 --> 00:16:17,510
It's been a while since you really
enjoyed yourself, hasn't it?

447
00:16:17,510 --> 00:16:18,710
There'll be one soon.

448
00:16:18,840 --> 00:16:20,390
Shengcheng is developing so fast.

449
00:16:20,390 --> 00:16:22,250
Everyone wants a slice of the pie.

450
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:25,030
Zhaohui,

451
00:16:25,680 --> 00:16:26,810
I know what you mean.

452
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:29,260
It's not that I won't help you.

453
00:16:29,630 --> 00:16:31,790
The Haihua matter isn't that simple.

454
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:33,530
Besides Meihua,

455
00:16:33,720 --> 00:16:35,390
Haihua has 3 other shareholders.

456
00:16:35,390 --> 00:16:37,250
One of them is Dongfeng Holdings.

457
00:16:37,390 --> 00:16:38,480
Mainland capital—

458
00:16:38,630 --> 00:16:39,390
as you know—

459
00:16:40,270 --> 00:16:41,550
is now competing fiercely

460
00:16:41,550 --> 00:16:42,750
with us.

461
00:16:44,390 --> 00:16:45,150
Is there anything you want

462
00:16:45,150 --> 00:16:46,550
that you can't get, Tang?

463
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:48,390
You're luckier than I am.

464
00:16:48,390 --> 00:16:49,270
You know my situation at home,

465
00:16:49,270 --> 00:16:50,080
don't you?

466
00:16:50,870 --> 00:16:51,870
If you help me,

467
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:53,240
in the future,

468
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:54,790
when I have more say,

469
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:56,800
I'll naturally help you too.

470
00:16:57,840 --> 00:16:58,720
Then you

471
00:16:58,720 --> 00:16:59,850
need to move faster.

472
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:02,770
The shareholders' meeting is on the 20th.

473
00:17:03,150 --> 00:17:04,589
I've reviewed your plan.

474
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:06,329
It was actually not bad.

475
00:17:07,310 --> 00:17:08,310
But rumor has it

476
00:17:08,480 --> 00:17:10,410
Dongfeng is modifying their plan.

477
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:11,480
So you guys

478
00:17:11,880 --> 00:17:14,010
might want to optimize yours further.

479
00:17:14,069 --> 00:17:14,510
Hua.

480
00:17:17,270 --> 00:17:18,109
As you know,

481
00:17:18,550 --> 00:17:20,280
I'm a straightforward person.

482
00:17:20,510 --> 00:17:21,550
I just want to know

483
00:17:21,880 --> 00:17:22,640
what expectations the shareholders

484
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:23,880
have for the hotel.

485
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:25,890
How should the plan be changed?

486
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:26,960
This is our company's

487
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:27,890
designer, Meng.

488
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:29,000
I brought him here today.

489
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:30,460
We hope for your guidance.

490
00:17:32,680 --> 00:17:33,340
Bartender.

491
00:17:39,830 --> 00:17:41,360
You're asking a favor of me,

492
00:17:41,590 --> 00:17:43,590
yet you picked such a strong liquor.

493
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:45,070
If I had gone easy,

494
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:47,130
would you have agreed to see me?

495
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:50,320
I like your personality.

496
00:17:51,880 --> 00:17:52,880
I'll be straight.

497
00:17:53,830 --> 00:17:54,640
Reviewing the proposals

498
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:56,240
is just a formality.

499
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:58,000
Your odds are good.

500
00:17:59,070 --> 00:18:00,000
Dongfeng found

501
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:01,960
a so-called "master" in the mainland.

502
00:18:01,960 --> 00:18:02,960
But their plan

503
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:05,590
is flawed from the start.

504
00:18:10,270 --> 00:18:10,830
Mr. Mao,

505
00:18:11,110 --> 00:18:12,000
are you going with me

506
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:13,130
to the bid tomorrow?

507
00:18:13,350 --> 00:18:14,150
I'm not going.

508
00:18:14,510 --> 00:18:15,770
I'm just a consultant.

509
00:18:16,230 --> 00:18:17,510
This is your own

510
00:18:17,510 --> 00:18:18,350
revised plan.

511
00:18:19,010 --> 00:18:20,450
The work I promised you

512
00:18:20,480 --> 00:18:22,550
is done as of today.

513
00:18:23,240 --> 00:18:25,500
I'm going back to the guesthouse to rest.

514
00:18:25,830 --> 00:18:26,200
Okay.

515
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:28,210
Ge Jian, see Mr. Mao out.

516
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:39,310
Mr. Mao still won't

517
00:18:39,310 --> 00:18:40,240
join the studio?

518
00:18:42,590 --> 00:18:44,240
Mr. Mao has been working
in Hangcheng Design Institute

519
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:44,960
for so many years.

520
00:18:44,960 --> 00:18:46,110
And he's retiring soon.

521
00:18:46,110 --> 00:18:47,960
It's understandable
he doesn't want the hassle.

522
00:18:47,960 --> 00:18:49,240
It's a pity, though.

523
00:18:49,590 --> 00:18:50,680
He seems to have

524
00:18:50,680 --> 00:18:51,440
a bad temper,

525
00:18:51,480 --> 00:18:51,790
but

526
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:53,640
he points out

527
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:55,100
the key issues every time.

528
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:59,730
Thank you all for your hard work
during this time.

529
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:00,880
Take

530
00:19:01,070 --> 00:19:02,270
the next two days off.

531
00:19:03,270 --> 00:19:05,530
-Thank you, Ms. Xia!
-Thank you, Ms. Xia!

532
00:19:07,920 --> 00:19:08,920
Goodbye, Ms. Xia.

533
00:19:08,920 --> 00:19:09,450
Goodbye.

534
00:19:09,720 --> 00:19:10,250
Goodbye.

535
00:19:10,720 --> 00:19:11,400
President Xia,

536
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:12,530
you're not leaving?

537
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:13,720
If you need anything,

538
00:19:13,720 --> 00:19:14,790
I can stay and help...

539
00:19:14,790 --> 00:19:15,880
No need.

540
00:19:15,960 --> 00:19:16,790
Goodbye, Ms. Xia!

541
00:19:16,790 --> 00:19:17,790
Goodbye, Ms. Xia!

542
00:19:18,030 --> 00:19:18,560
Bye-bye.

543
00:19:20,830 --> 00:19:22,230
The bidding is tomorrow.

544
00:19:22,400 --> 00:19:24,030
You need to familiarize yourself
with the plan, right?

545
00:19:24,030 --> 00:19:24,790
Yes.

546
00:19:24,960 --> 00:19:26,360
I need to go over it again.

547
00:19:26,440 --> 00:19:26,880
Okay.

548
00:19:27,620 --> 00:19:28,860
You go over the plan,

549
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:30,460
and I'll go over the files.

550
00:19:30,680 --> 00:19:31,610
If we are hungry,

551
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:32,920
there's roast goose.

552
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:34,000
And if we're thirsty,

553
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:34,930
there are Cokes.

554
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:37,130
Well, Ms. Xia?

555
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:38,680
Are you satisfied

556
00:19:38,830 --> 00:19:40,160
with this arrangement?

557
00:19:40,510 --> 00:19:41,440
Very satisfied.

558
00:19:42,680 --> 00:19:43,880
If you're satisfied,

559
00:19:44,590 --> 00:19:45,650
after the bidding,

560
00:19:45,830 --> 00:19:46,880
can you give me

561
00:19:47,300 --> 00:19:49,030
my "employment certificate"?

562
00:19:51,880 --> 00:19:52,540
Zhou Cheng,

563
00:19:53,030 --> 00:19:54,270
I make you wait every time.

564
00:19:54,270 --> 00:19:54,870
I promise,

565
00:19:55,160 --> 00:19:56,070
never again.

566
00:19:59,070 --> 00:19:59,440
Okay.

567
00:20:07,310 --> 00:20:08,170
I like this one.

568
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:11,460
Morning, Mr. Tang.

569
00:20:11,550 --> 00:20:12,280
You're here.

570
00:20:12,720 --> 00:20:13,320
You may go.

571
00:20:14,750 --> 00:20:15,880
That Manager Huo...

572
00:20:16,480 --> 00:20:18,350
I tried to arrange a meeting
with him several times.

573
00:20:18,350 --> 00:20:20,480
He's so difficult to get an appointment
with. So hard to deal with.

574
00:20:20,480 --> 00:20:22,720
I'd like to see him for myself today.

575
00:20:28,590 --> 00:20:29,190
He's here.

576
00:20:29,400 --> 00:20:30,400
See for yourself.

577
00:20:30,510 --> 00:20:31,920
Exactly the type I hate.

578
00:20:40,030 --> 00:20:40,560
Morning,

579
00:20:40,790 --> 00:20:41,520
Manager Huo.

580
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:42,240
Morning.

581
00:20:42,240 --> 00:20:43,030
Which design company

582
00:20:43,030 --> 00:20:44,090
