Boss.

869
00:30:41,400 --> 00:30:42,570
That Gangdao merchant was so shocked

870
00:30:42,570 --> 00:30:44,630
that he was completely dumbfounded.

871
00:30:49,030 --> 00:30:49,590
Mr. Mao.

872
00:30:50,510 --> 00:30:52,200
For this 30-million project,

873
00:30:52,440 --> 00:30:53,480
you gave us

874
00:30:53,480 --> 00:30:54,750
a lot of help.

875
00:30:57,160 --> 00:30:58,790
Do you think I'm angry?

876
00:30:59,790 --> 00:31:01,680
Am I that petty?

877
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:03,350
It's just that...

878
00:31:03,680 --> 00:31:05,590
you seem a bit unhappy.

879
00:31:06,640 --> 00:31:07,510
As you know,

880
00:31:08,510 --> 00:31:09,510
Xiaolan

881
00:31:09,960 --> 00:31:11,790
kept me here as a designer

882
00:31:12,550 --> 00:31:14,750
and wanted me to be her teacher.

883
00:31:15,920 --> 00:31:16,880
Do you think

884
00:31:17,830 --> 00:31:19,030
I could agree to that?

885
00:31:23,750 --> 00:31:25,030
To be honest,

886
00:31:25,510 --> 00:31:28,040
after spending time with Xiaolan
these days,

887
00:31:28,110 --> 00:31:30,000
I really like this girl.

888
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:33,000
She is gifted and talented.

889
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:34,680
Most importantly,

890
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:36,830
she has courage and boldness.

891
00:31:37,720 --> 00:31:39,070
Architecture

892
00:31:39,070 --> 00:31:41,110
is not dead. It is alive.

893
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:43,550
It should grow with the city

894
00:31:43,750 --> 00:31:45,160
and the people.

895
00:31:45,920 --> 00:31:47,160
Xiaolan is so young,

896
00:31:47,160 --> 00:31:48,550
yet she has such vision.

897
00:31:48,750 --> 00:31:50,810
Who wouldn't like a student like her?

898
00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:54,810
Then what are you hesitating for, Mr. Mao?

899
00:31:55,160 --> 00:31:56,200
I am hesitating because,

900
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:58,550
regarding this 30-million project,

901
00:31:58,920 --> 00:32:00,440
she sees further

902
00:32:00,590 --> 00:32:01,880
than all of us.

903
00:32:03,160 --> 00:32:04,160
I'm old.

904
00:32:04,440 --> 00:32:06,040
How much more can I teach her?

905
00:32:07,070 --> 00:32:08,550
Mr. Mao.

906
00:32:09,590 --> 00:32:10,480
Both proposals

907
00:32:10,640 --> 00:32:11,750
were modified based on

908
00:32:11,750 --> 00:32:12,720
your foundation.

909
00:32:12,720 --> 00:32:13,790
If I were to

910
00:32:14,000 --> 00:32:15,350
start completely from scratch

911
00:32:15,350 --> 00:32:16,720
and create a five-star hotel's

912
00:32:16,720 --> 00:32:17,400
design plan on my own,

913
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:19,000
I definitely couldn't do it.

914
00:32:20,110 --> 00:32:21,510
Now you're being modest.

915
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:23,640
It's true.

916
00:32:24,030 --> 00:32:25,760
Your knowledge and experience

917
00:32:26,240 --> 00:32:27,920
are something I could never catch up to,

918
00:32:27,920 --> 00:32:28,960
even if I spent

919
00:32:28,960 --> 00:32:30,420
ten-plus years studying.

920
00:32:30,830 --> 00:32:31,590
Mr. Mao,

921
00:32:32,150 --> 00:32:33,410
I just have foresight,

922
00:32:33,790 --> 00:32:35,200
but I haven't actually walked

923
00:32:35,200 --> 00:32:36,130
much of the path.

924
00:32:37,480 --> 00:32:38,240
So, Mr. Mao,

925
00:32:38,960 --> 00:32:40,480
I really need you.

926
00:32:42,710 --> 00:32:44,110
I want to be your student.

927
00:32:45,920 --> 00:32:47,200
To be my student,

928
00:32:47,620 --> 00:32:49,970
you'd have to kowtow formally.

929
00:32:50,350 --> 00:32:51,010
No problem.

930
00:32:54,590 --> 00:32:55,640
I'll take you.

931
00:32:58,470 --> 00:33:01,530
Congratulations, Ms. Xia!
Congratulations, Mr. Mao!

932
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:04,970
Congratulations, Mr. Mao!

933
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:05,920
So you guys

934
00:33:06,160 --> 00:33:07,310
planned it all out.

935
00:33:14,240 --> 00:33:15,880
Tomorrow, I'll go to Dongfeng first.

936
00:33:15,880 --> 00:33:17,070
You go to the law firm.

937
00:33:17,070 --> 00:33:17,640
Then in the afternoon,

938
00:33:17,640 --> 00:33:18,880
let's meet at the Civil Affairs Bureau.

939
00:33:18,880 --> 00:33:19,210
Okay.

940
00:33:20,030 --> 00:33:21,240
After we get the certificate,

941
00:33:21,240 --> 00:33:22,750
let's have dinner together.

942
00:33:22,750 --> 00:33:24,750
Let's invite Wei and Zhenzhu along.

943
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:25,830
Okay.

944
00:33:27,490 --> 00:33:29,480
Why is Mr. Zhou,
who's usually so sharp-tongued,

945
00:33:29,480 --> 00:33:30,940
only saying "okay" today?

946
00:33:31,440 --> 00:33:32,700
As long as I'm with you,

947
00:33:33,110 --> 00:33:34,710
everything seems fine to me.

948
00:33:36,310 --> 00:33:37,640
Mr. Mao once asked me,

949
00:33:38,310 --> 00:33:39,030
as

950
00:33:39,310 --> 00:33:41,240
a one-in-a-million lucky person,

951
00:33:41,510 --> 00:33:42,920
what right I had to pave the way

952
00:33:42,920 --> 00:33:44,240
for others' futures.

953
00:33:45,080 --> 00:33:47,000
I remember the first time
I went to Longcheng

954
00:33:47,000 --> 00:33:48,270
and met Bai Zhenzhu.

955
00:33:48,510 --> 00:33:49,160
I told her

956
00:33:49,160 --> 00:33:51,070
she could set up a stall in Shengcheng,

957
00:33:51,070 --> 00:33:52,030
and I really thought of myself

958
00:33:52,030 --> 00:33:53,160
as a savior.

959
00:33:53,750 --> 00:33:54,880
Later I realized,

960
00:33:55,350 --> 00:33:56,350
maybe without me,

961
00:33:56,680 --> 00:33:58,590
they would have succeeded anyway.

962
00:33:58,590 --> 00:34:00,440
Just by a different path,

963
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:02,270
or at a different time.

964
00:34:03,200 --> 00:34:05,400
I'm actually not that important at all.

965
00:34:06,440 --> 00:34:07,840
To other people's lives,

966
00:34:08,440 --> 00:34:10,440
of course we aren't that important.

967
00:34:11,360 --> 00:34:12,440
But you don't need to

968
00:34:12,440 --> 00:34:13,400
completely deny

969
00:34:13,400 --> 00:34:14,530
your contribution.

970
00:34:15,110 --> 00:34:16,710
You really did help Zhenzhu.

971
00:34:16,840 --> 00:34:18,100
And you helped Wei too.

972
00:34:18,440 --> 00:34:19,300
But similarly,

973
00:34:19,710 --> 00:34:20,840
they helped you too.

974
00:34:21,679 --> 00:34:22,320
We have long since

975
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:23,380
left deep marks

976
00:34:23,880 --> 00:34:25,190
in each other's lives.

977
00:34:26,360 --> 00:34:27,760
They can never be erased.

978
00:34:28,880 --> 00:34:30,230
If I disappear,

979
00:34:31,150 --> 00:34:33,030
will those marks still exist?

980
00:34:35,190 --> 00:34:35,989
What's wrong?

981
00:34:36,360 --> 00:34:37,710
Why are you suddenly looking at me

982
00:34:37,710 --> 00:34:39,040
with such adoring eyes?

983
00:34:42,630 --> 00:34:44,230
Sometimes I really feel like

984
00:34:44,800 --> 00:34:45,440
there are

985
00:34:46,230 --> 00:34:47,670
2 souls in here.

986
00:34:48,510 --> 00:34:49,920
One is the current you,

987
00:34:50,440 --> 00:34:51,190
and the other

988
00:34:51,510 --> 00:34:53,110
is a very mature old soul.

989
00:34:56,070 --> 00:34:56,800
Oh, no.

990
00:34:57,510 --> 00:34:58,510
You think I'm old.

991
00:34:58,930 --> 00:34:59,630
I remember when we

992
00:34:59,630 --> 00:35:00,480
first met,

993
00:35:00,480 --> 00:35:02,190
didn't you think I was childish?

994
00:35:02,190 --> 00:35:03,550
You're still childish now.

995
00:35:03,550 --> 00:35:04,480
Childish and old

996
00:35:04,630 --> 00:35:05,960
aren't contradictory.

997
00:35:06,440 --> 00:35:07,370
Then tomorrow,

998
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:09,630
do you want a childish me

999
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:10,880
or an old me?

1000
00:35:13,070 --> 00:35:14,760
I want

1001
00:35:15,710 --> 00:35:16,570
a handsome you.

1002
00:35:18,000 --> 00:35:18,530
Alright.

1003
00:35:18,710 --> 00:35:20,070
Then just wait and see.

1004
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:21,190
Okay.

1005
00:35:34,630 --> 00:35:35,190
Zhenzhu.

1006
00:35:36,230 --> 00:35:38,070
Why do you look more anxious than I do?

1007
00:35:38,070 --> 00:35:39,110
Aren't you anxious?

1008
00:35:39,110 --> 00:35:40,670
I don't believe you're not anxious.

1009
00:35:40,670 --> 00:35:41,710
Why isn't Cheng here yet?

1010
00:35:41,710 --> 00:35:42,880
Did something happen on the way

1011
00:35:42,880 --> 00:35:43,440
that delayed him?

1012
00:35:43,440 --> 00:35:44,300
Did he call you?

1013
00:35:44,920 --> 00:35:47,000
No call means he's fine.

1014
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:48,810
Let's wait a bit longer.

1015
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:53,400
Xiaolan.

1016
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:55,420
Something happened to Cheng.

1017
00:35:55,550 --> 00:35:56,750
He's in the hospital.

1018
00:35:57,950 --> 00:35:58,800
What happened?

1019
00:35:58,800 --> 00:35:59,360
Xiaolan!

1020
00:36:01,030 --> 00:36:02,490
Why do the people I cherish

1021
00:36:02,840 --> 00:36:05,400
always get into trouble
at the most important moments?

1022
00:36:05,400 --> 00:36:06,530
Once is an accident.

1023
00:36:06,840 --> 00:36:08,170
But twice? Three times?

1024
00:36:09,630 --> 00:36:12,030
And my increasingly confused memories...

1025
00:36:12,840 --> 00:36:14,320
All of this makes me suspect

1026
00:36:13,090 --> 00:36:16,270
[In Operation]

1027
00:36:14,710 --> 00:36:16,320
that I've stayed here too long,

1028
00:36:16,320 --> 00:36:17,160
done too much,

1029
00:36:17,440 --> 00:36:19,840
and affected the balance
of time and space.

1030
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:21,620
Zhou Cheng.

1031
00:36:22,920 --> 00:36:24,550
Please be fine.

1032
00:36:24,960 --> 00:36:25,670
Make way!

1033
00:37:29,510 --> 00:37:30,280
I'm fine.

1034
00:37:59,590 --> 00:38:00,190
Jiang Yan!

1035
00:38:02,510 --> 00:38:03,110
Jiang Yan!

1036
00:38:03,960 --> 00:38:06,280
Jiang Yan! Jiang Yan! Jiang Yan!

1037
00:38:11,760 --> 00:38:12,360
Jiang Yan!

1038
00:38:24,400 --> 00:38:25,000
Jiang Yan!

1039
00:38:25,670 --> 00:38:26,730
Jiang Yan, wake up!

1040
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:31,280
Get up, Jiang Yan!

1041
00:38:43,070 --> 00:38:44,410
Leave me. Go!

1042
00:39:02,710 --> 00:39:03,240
Xiaolan.

1043
00:39:05,440 --> 00:39:06,900
I'm actually very scared.

1044
00:39:08,110 --> 00:39:08,960
From Shi Kai,

1045
00:39:10,480 --> 00:39:11,230
to Jiang Yan—

1046
00:39:12,920 --> 00:39:13,630
if I hadn't insisted

1047
00:39:13,630 --> 00:39:15,760
on investigating the fisherman case,

1048
00:39:16,630 --> 00:39:17,230
and if I hadn't insisted

1049
00:39:17,230 --> 00:39:18,230
on digging deeper,

1050
00:39:18,230 --> 00:39:19,110
maybe they wouldn't have...

1051
00:39:19,110 --> 00:39:19,770
Zhou Cheng.

1052
00:39:20,550 --> 00:39:21,440
You wanted to get justice

1053
00:39:21,440 --> 00:39:22,480
for Shi Kai.

1054
00:39:23,400 --> 00:39:24,460
That wasn't wrong.

1055
00:39:26,550 --> 00:39:27,190
Trust me.

1056
00:39:28,630 --> 00:39:29,830
It was not your fault.

1057
00:39:38,590 --> 00:39:41,480
Kang Wei, Shi Kai, and Jiang Yan.

1058
00:39:42,190 --> 00:39:44,030
These bizarre events

1059
00:39:44,670 --> 00:39:46,670
have made Zhou Cheng blame himself.

1060
00:39:47,280 --> 00:39:49,000
I know it's not his fault.

1061
00:39:50,320 --> 00:39:51,710
All of this

1062
00:39:52,630 --> 00:39:54,590
is probably related to my arrival.

1063
00:39:56,190 --> 00:39:57,360
But I can't

1064
00:39:57,710 --> 00:39:59,570
tell Zhou Cheng about my worries.

1065
00:40:00,710 --> 00:40:02,920
I just hope he stays safe,

1066
00:40:03,630 --> 00:40:05,880
and these things stop happening.

1067
00:40:07,510 --> 00:40:08,190
Be careful.

1068
00:40:13,550 --> 00:40:15,070
The surgery went smoothly.

1069
00:40:15,070 --> 00:40:15,880
The doctor said

1070
00:40:15,880 --> 00:40:17,340
Jiang Yan is out of danger.

1071
00:40:18,070 --> 00:40:19,150
But the burns on her back

1072
00:40:19,150 --> 00:40:20,150
are quite severe.

1073
00:40:21,030 --> 00:40:22,230
We aren't her family.

1074
00:40:22,880 --> 00:40:23,960
Her future treatment

1075
00:40:23,960 --> 00:40:25,840
requires her parents' involvement.

1076
00:40:25,840 --> 00:40:27,440
I've already notified them.

1077
00:40:28,630 --> 00:40:30,630
You are Zhou Cheng from Bed 2, right?

1078
00:40:30,850 --> 00:40:31,160
Yes.

1079
00:40:31,190 --> 00:40:32,490
Visiting hours are over.

1080
00:40:32,490 --> 00:40:35,220
Non-family members,
please leave immediately.

1081
00:40:35,850 --> 00:40:36,590
Family members only.

1082
00:40:36,590 --> 00:40:37,650
Are you her family?

1083
00:40:38,820 --> 00:40:40,130
I... sort of am.

1084
00:40:40,670 --> 00:40:41,440
Sort of?

1085
00:40:41,630 --> 00:40:42,710
So you're not, then.

1086
00:40:42,710 --> 00:40:43,840
Come back tomorrow.

1087
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:45,480
It's okay.

1088
00:40:45,960 --> 00:40:46,960
You go back first.

1089
00:40:51,360 --> 00:40:51,760
Okay.

1090
00:40:52,360 --> 00:40:53,420
I'll head off then.

1091
00:40:53,630 --> 00:40:54,000
Okay.

1092
00:41:00,840 --> 00:41:02,110
I'm leaving now.

1093
00:41:02,710 --> 00:41:04,110
I'll come back tomorrow.

1094
00:41:04,360 --> 00:41:04,760
Okay.

1095
00:41:21,480 --> 00:41:22,140
Zhou Cheng,

1096
00:41:22,320 --> 00:41:24,180
you should go back and rest early.

1097
00:41:48,350 --> 00:41:48,920
Ms. Xia.

1098
00:41:50,150 --> 00:41:51,710
Are you going to the office
tomorrow morning?

1099
00:41:51,710 --> 00:41:52,910
Come early tomorrow.

1100
00:41:53,150 --> 00:41:54,400
We'll go to the company first,
then the hospital.

1101
00:41:54,400 --> 00:41:54,840
Got it.
